			title: "filter_media_scanning.go timeout will crash policyserver if media download takes more than 30s",
			body: "### I am a...\n\nPolicyserv operator with logs to help fix a bug\n\n### Description\n\nI dont feel confident enough to make a PR for this and im certainly no go expert, so here is how claude explained it to me :)\n\n_\n\n> CheckEvent closes the per-media result channels in a deferred cleanup when its collection loop returns (notably on read-timeout), but the scanMedia goroutines that outlive that return still send on those channels, causing panic: send on closed channel. Buffered channels here don't need closing at all; removing the close eliminates the race.\n\n_\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n- send media into a room from a server that wont be able to provide that media within 30 seconds\n\nin HA-proxy this is easily done by adding something like this:\n```\n    acl matrix_media_endpoints path_reg ^/_matrix/client/v1/media/\n    acl matrix_media_endpoints path_reg ^/_matrix/federation/v1/media/\n    http-request pause 31s if matrix_media_endpoints\n```\n\n### Installation Method\n\nOther (please mention below)\n\n### Homeserver\n\ncodestorm.net\n\n### Policyserv Server Name\n\n/\n\n### Policyserv Version\n\n1.6.0\n\n### Affected Filters\n\nMedia scanning\n\n### Relevant log output\n\n```shell\n2026-06-03 13:24:23.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta systemd[1]: policyserv.service: Scheduled restart job, restart counter is at 3.\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta systemd[1]: policyserv.service: Consumed 3.854s CPU time, 17.3M memory peak.\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta systemd[1]: policyserv.service: Failed with result 'exit-code'.\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta systemd[1]: policyserv.service: Main process exited, code=exited, status=2/INVALIDARGUMENT\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: #011/opt/policyserv/filter/filter_media_scanning.go:67 +0x1bf\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: created by github.com/matrix-org/policyserv/filter.(*InstancedMediaScanningFilter).CheckEvent in goroutine 4733\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: #011/opt/policyserv/filter/filter_media_scanning.go:106 +0x78b\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: github.com/matrix-org/policyserv/filter.(*InstancedMediaScanningFilter).scanMedia(0x381161a80f60, {0x124aba8, 0x381161f84770}, {0x12628c8, 0x381161bdb340}, 0x3811621c2fc0, 0x381161c158f0)\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: goroutine 4734 [running]:\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: panic: send on closed channel\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: [policyserv] 2026/06/03 13:24:18.328701 filter_media_scanning.go:105: [$MEpqttsfWYjhUuebSh-tQ04qom4YUSz-Oxo6SQJyOcw | !ef0cr1yG9c2icC6jmBQpMTXIK97vt7VQlLOb_7d1BnY] Error downloading media: Get \"https://matrix.codestorm.net/_matrix/client/v1/media/download/bi-vibes.com/KOZaUjcBuFfOOtGeYxNGYTSs\": context deadline exceeded\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: timed out waiting for media scanning results}): context canceled\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: [policyserv] 2026/06/03 13:24:18.328057 pool.go:101: [$MEpqttsfWYjhUuebSh-tQ04qom4YUSz-Oxo6SQJyOcw | !ef0cr1yG9c2icC6jmBQpMTXIK97vt7VQlLOb_7d1BnY] Result channel closed, not sending result (&{Vectors:map[] IsProbablySpam:false Err:error at group 2\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: timed out waiting for media scanning results\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: [policyserv] 2026/06/03 13:24:18.327658 pool.go:146: [$MEpqttsfWYjhUuebSh-tQ04qom4YUSz-Oxo6SQJyOcw | !ef0cr1yG9c2icC6jmBQpMTXIK97vt7VQlLOb_7d1BnY] Result from singleflight: <nil>, error at group 2\n2026-06-03 13:24:18.000\tpolicyserv-beta\npolicyserv-beta policyserv[58252]: [policyserv] 2026/06/03 13:24:18.316566 r",
